101
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,000
Okay.

102
00:05:27,000 --> 00:05:31,000
And I grew up with that knowledge of treating people like you would have them treat you.

103
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,000
Okay.

104
